    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Available is a mechanically sound E46 M3 featuring the legendary S54 3.2L naturally aspirated inline-six, renowned for its 8,000 RPM redline and individual throttle bodies. This example is equipped with a 6-speed Getrag manual gearbox and a factory limited-slip differential. Critical preventative maintenance has been addressed, including rear subframe reinforcement and a comprehensive VANOS system overhaul. The suspension geometry remains precise, bolstered by upgraded polyurethane bushings and refreshed dampers. While the exterior displays honest patina reflective of its 'good' condition, the drivetrain remains exceptionally tight, delivering linear power and the signature metallic rasp of the S54. A true driver's car with a focus on tactile feedback and mechanical longevity.",
